data.description: Step into the warmth of comfort in this beautifully remodeled Cape Cod home, where every corner whispers tales of timeless charm and modern luxury.  This home has enough space for everyone with 5 bedrooms and full bathroom on each level.   A paradise for entertaining, the large finished basement and fenced in back yard oasis provide enough space for holiday gatherings and summer BBQs with your family and friends.  With its enchanting atmosphere, this home is a canvas for the cherished moments that become lifelong memories. Your perfect haven awaits!
